---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@components/Container.astro";
import Link from "@components/Link.astro";
---

<Layout title="News" description="Latest news and features about Scott Lingner's creative work.">
  <Container>
    <aside data-pagefind-ignore>
      <h1 class="animate text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100 mb-4">
        News
      </h1>
      <p class="animate text-lg text-stone-700 dark:text-stone-300 mb-12">
        Features and highlights from across my creative work.
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-12">
        <article class="animate space-y-8">
          <div class="bg-stone-200/50 dark:bg-stone-800/50 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-lg border border-stone-300/50 dark:border-stone-700/50">
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100 mb-6">
              Spiral Pigeon Bird House - San Diego Art Project
            </h2>

            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="prose prose-stone dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
                <p class="text-stone-700 dark:text-stone-300">
                  A sculptural house for pigeons built in San Diego, featuring hollow rectangular cubes attached in a spiral formation around a central pole. This public art project combines creativity, craftsmanship, and urban wildlife habitat design.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-800 dark:text-stone-200">Video</h3>

                <div class="aspect-video rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md">
                  <iframe
                    width="100%"
                    height="100%"
                    src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mFP0CE-PONk"
                    title="YouTube video player"
                    frameborder="0"
                    allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
                    allowfullscreen
                    class="w-full h-full"
                  ></iframe>
                </div>

                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-800 dark:text-stone-200 mt-8">Design & Build Process</h3>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                  <img
                    src="/pigeon-1.png"
                    alt="Spiral Pigeon Bird House - Initial Design"
                    class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-md"
                  />
                  <img
                    src="/pigeon-1a.png"
                    alt="Spiral Pigeon Bird House - Construction"
                    class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-md"
                  />
                  <img
                    src="/pigeon-2.png"
                    alt="Spiral Pigeon Bird House - Backyard Build"
                    class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-md"
                  />
                </div>

                <div class="prose prose-stone dark:prose-invert max-w-none mt-6">
                  <p class="text-stone-700 dark:text-stone-300">
                    <strong>About the Project:</strong> The design mimics the natural cliff-side habitat of pigeons with individual protected nesting boxes. Each box features an open front for easy access, with the spiral arrangement providing both aesthetic appeal and predator protection. Built with wood and metal in my San Diego backyard, the structure incorporates natural elements like twigs and wooden leaves to create authentic nesting spaces.
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-stone-700 dark:text-stone-300">
                    The project involved collaboration with artists and scientists to optimize the design for pigeon colonization. Discussions covered box size, placement height, predator protection, and environmental integration. Scientists noted that pigeons are highly intelligent birds that prefer high, protected spaces mimicking their natural cliff habitat. Artists provided feedback on making the openings smaller to protect nesting birds from cats and other predators.
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-stone-700 dark:text-stone-300">
                    The modular design allows for varied box sizes and creates a visually striking sculptural element in the urban landscape. Natural materials were added to encourage colonization, and the structure was positioned to provide both safety and access to food sources.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="animate space-y-8">
          <div class="bg-stone-200/50 dark:bg-stone-800/50 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-lg border border-stone-300/50 dark:border-stone-700/50">
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100 mb-6">
              Homemade Instruments & Musical Creations
            </h2>

            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="prose prose-stone dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
                <p class="text-stone-700 dark:text-stone-300">
                  My homemade instruments and experimental music projects have been featured across various platforms, showcasing the intersection of creativity, craftsmanship, and sound.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-800 dark:text-stone-200">Videos</h3>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                  <div class="aspect-video rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md">
                    <iframe
                      width="100%"
                      height="100%"
                      src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9fj4IEqcPJ4"
                      title="YouTube video player"
                      frameborder="0"
                      allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
                      allowfullscreen
                      class="w-full h-full"
                    ></iframe>
                  </div>

                  <div class="aspect-video rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md">
                    <iframe
                      width="100%"
                      height="100%"
                      src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Nlb4VGykGeU"
                      title="YouTube video player"
                      frameborder="0"
                      allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
                      allowfullscreen
                      class="w-full h-full"
                    ></iframe>
                  </div>

                  <div class="aspect-video rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md md:col-span-2">
                    <iframe
                      width="100%"
                      height="100%"
                      src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/AD4y2y79LVY"
                      title="YouTube video player"
                      frameborder="0"
                      allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
                      allowfullscreen
                      class="w-full h-full"
                    ></iframe>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-800 dark:text-stone-200 mt-8">Featured In</h3>

                <div class="space-y-4">
                  <Link
                    href="https://www.cnet.com/pictures/homemade-instruments-worth-singing-about-pictures/"
                    external
                    class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-stone-300/50 dark:border-stone-700/50 hover:bg-stone-300/50 dark:hover:bg-stone-700/50 transition-colors"
                  >
                    <div class="font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">
                      CNET: "Homemade instruments worth singing about"
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-sm text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 mt-1">
                      A feature showcasing unique homemade musical instruments
                    </div>
                  </Link>

                  <Link
                    href="https://www.booooooom.com/2012/09/05/made-of-imagination-homemade-instrument-submissions/"
                    external
                    class="block p-4 rounded-lg border border-stone-300/50 dark:border-stone-700/50 hover:bg-stone-300/50 dark:hover:bg-stone-700/50 transition-colors"
                  >
                    <div class="font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">
                      BOOOOOOOM: "Made of Imagination: Homemade Instrument Submissions"
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-sm text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 mt-1">
                      Featured in a collection of creative homemade instruments from artists worldwide
                    </div>
                  </Link>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </Container>
</Layout>
